Don't Look Down is the second studio album by American singer-songwriter Skylar Grey. It was released on July 5, 2013, by KidinaKorner and Interscope Records. The album's production was primarily handled by Alex da Kid and J.R. Rotem along with being executive produced by Eminem. Guest appearances on the album include Big Sean, Eminem, Travis Barker and Angel Haze.
